        <item>
            <title>【评测】Sony A1 II 旗舰级相机，对焦、追踪效能超强 + 高像素除杂讯超强</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/21/sony-a1-ii-review/dc/dc-test/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-a1-ii-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/21/sony-a1-ii-review/dc/dc-test/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 10:34:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相机测试]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony A1 II]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1284606</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony 推出全新旗舰级相机 Sony A1 II。作为旗舰相机，操控性、自动对焦、稳定性等方面进行了改良，用上最新影像引擎，保持高达每秒 30 张快门，而且在高感光度相片上，发挥出色的低杂讯表现。今次我们就会实试旗舰机在拍摄人像相片时的效果，还有高感光度下的杂讯表现。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288000" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04521-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04521-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04521.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287999" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04495-532x580.jpg" alt="" width="532" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04495-532x580.jpg 532w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04495.jpg 825w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 532px" /></p><p>Sony 旗舰级相机 Sony A1 II 拥有超强性能与灵活性，5000 万像素全片幅感光元件加快了快速读取性能，在提供高画质相片之下，大容量的连拍快取迎合长时间高速连拍。而且感光元件在色彩还原能力更强，除迎合风景相片、商业相片的拍摄需要，也适合高阶摄影爱好者。</p><p><a title="DSC00052" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54243626001/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54243626001_7a27f1dcde_b.jpg" alt="DSC00052" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="DSC00744" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54243851423/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54243851423_351158954a_b.jpg" alt="DSC00744" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC00854" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54242719327/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54242719327_6c46741aa4_b.jpg" alt="DSC00854" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC00754" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54243852888/in/album-72177720322935207/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54243852888_e4d0869b42_b.jpg" alt="DSC00754" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="DSC00726" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54243856499/in/album-72177720322935207/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54243856499_d4cf936652_b.jpg" alt="DSC00726" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>A1 II 在色彩捕捉的能力更强</p><p><a title="DSC00667" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54243854244/in/album-72177720322935207/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54243854244_2a0a95ccea_b.jpg" alt="DSC00667" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>放大墙身的红砖感受到相机与镜头的总合解像力</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288001" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04498-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04498-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04498.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Sony A1 II 外观设计注重细节改良，相较于前代机型，握把设计更深更舒适，操控按键更加现代化，特别是自订按键与自动对焦操控杆。在机顶的各个转盘，你可直接控制：</p><p>摄影模式</p><p>拍片／影相／慢动作录影</p><p>定格／连拍／高速连拍／倒数拍摄</p><p>自动对焦／手动对焦／连续对焦</p><p>3 个自订转盘，控制快门 ISO 等参数</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288002" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04511-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04511-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04511.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288003" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04510-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04510-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04510.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>新款相机延续了 Sony 现代化选单系统，上述的 5 个转盘中有 3 个有锁定按键，在专业摄影师忙碌的拍摄工作中，避免误操作的出现。机身除转盘外，亦拥有 Joysick、C1 至到 C4 共 4 个自订功能按键，独立录影按键等。机身连接性一如旗舰级别，包括咪高风插口、耳机插口、有线网络插口、PC 同步插口、全尺寸的 HDMI 插口与快速充电功能，应对专业拍摄需求。记忆卡插槽支援双 CFexpress Type A 与 SD 卡，确保用家自由选择储存媒体，适合稳定高速连拍、8K 影片摄录的需求。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288004" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04506-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04506-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04506.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288005" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04507-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04507-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04507.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288009" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04542-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04542-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04542.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>显示与稳定性能改进</h2><p>新款相机配备全新 4 方向旋转屏幕及更高解像度的显示器，从前代的 1.44 百万像素提升至 2 百万像素，并提供更高亮度，适合摄影与录影使用。电子观景器仍保留 9.44 百万像素高解像度，显示清晰细腻。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288013" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04558-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04558-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc04558.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次测试相片使用 Sony 最新推出的 FE 28-50mm F2 GM</p><p><a title="DSC00525" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54244046795/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54244046795_b59c19a01e_b.jpg" alt="DSC00525" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="DSC00143" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54244045625/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54244045625_2df0a31fe9_b.jpg" alt="DSC00143" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="DSC00495" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54242724342/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54242724342_b812306bf1_b.jpg" alt="DSC00495" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="DSC00591" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54244046980/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54244046980_4dfa56ef90_b.jpg" alt="DSC00591" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;"><p>Sony A1 II 内建的新一代五轴影像稳定系统带来平均 7.5 至 8 级的机身防震效果，相较于前代的 5.5 级有显著提升，使得低速快门拍摄更加稳定。在晚间摄影时，我们很多相片都用上低速快门、低感光度拍摄，靠机身防震效果，获得更为清晰、画质更高的相片。而在高感度方面，A1 II 有更强的细腻度表现。</p><p><a title="DSC00780" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54242717882/in/album-72177720322935207/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54242717882_3e5826d276_b.jpg" alt="DSC00780" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>ISO 1600</p><p><a title="DSC00819" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54242718682/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54242718682_78f3b2e19f_b.jpg" alt="DSC00819" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>ISO 2500</p><p><a title="DSC00756" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54243858884/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54243858884_bc56104355_b.jpg" alt="DSC00756" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>ISO 3200</p><p><a title="DSC00864" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54244042720/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54244042720_5e74eb005a_b.jpg" alt="DSC00864" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>ISO 3200</p><p><a title="DSC00813" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54244040935/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54244040935_eb6707b589_b.jpg" alt="DSC00813" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>ISO 4000</p><p><a title="DSC00723" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54244036385/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54244036385_5b7c6de29f_b.jpg" alt="DSC00723" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>ISO 4000</p><p><a title="DSC00776" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54243621506/in/album-72177720322935207/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54243621506_520f4ef5ff_b.jpg" alt="DSC00776" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>ISO 4000</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a title="DSC00847" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54242719297/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54242719297_c754c6f213_b.jpg" alt="DSC00847" width="683" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>ISO 10000</p><p><a title="DSC00842" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54242719212/in/album-72177720322935207/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54242719212_ca787dd938_b.jpg" alt="DSC00842" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script>ISO 12800</p><h2>感光元件与性能表现</h2><p>Sony A1 II 沿用了前代的 5000 万像素感光元件，读取速度仍然超快。机械快门可达到 1/400 秒的闪光同步速度，电子快门则提供极低的滚动快门效应与快速连拍能力，最高可达每秒 30 张连拍。</p><p>我们就在早前记者会的高速连拍的相片测试中，利用高速连拍捕捉到运动员动作之中最精彩一刻。</p><p><a title="20241120-4CY04985" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54153144175/in/album-72177720322935207" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54153144175_c4fc78efd2_b.jpg" alt="20241120-4CY04985" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="20241120-4CY05035" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54153144030/in/album-72177720322935207/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54153144030_babaf403d0_b.jpg" alt="20241120-4CY05035" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="20241120-4CY04971" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54153012654/in/album-72177720322935207/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54153012654_c7a54c2d80_b.jpg" alt="20241120-4CY04971" width="1024" height="683" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
