            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>现时 Apple App Store 上有不少 AI 机械人应用程式，但这些 AI 机械人 App 质素良莠不齐，部分 App 或会盗取你的个人资料。今日小编想和大家分享一个无须连接网络，能够直接在本机运行的 LLM 语言 App「fullmoon: local intelligence」，支援 Llama 3.2 最新 3b 及 1b 模型，最重要的是这个 App 可免费使用，下载后可在 app 内选择不同模型，然后直接使用。</p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="OUTPUT" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1048799333?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p style="text-align: center;"><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script><br />
▲无须连接网络，开启飞航模式 + 关 Wi-Fi 也可用</p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="IMG_0071" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1048795850?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲回复快捷迅速</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287787" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1196-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1196-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1196.png 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可要求它为你制定减肥方案</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287788" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1197-535x580.png" alt="" width="535" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1197-535x580.png 535w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1197.png 830w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲也可查询投资意见</p><h2>Step 1 下载应用程式</h2><p>到 App Store 将应用程式下载到你的 iPhone 或 iPad。</p><p>应用程式名称：fullmoon: local intelligence</p><p>下载连结：<a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/id6727014156">https://apps.apple.com/app/id6727014156</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287766" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_0067-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_0067-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_0067.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲先下载 fullmoon: local intelligence 应用程式</p><h2>Step 2 下载模型</h2><p>下载完应用程式后，你需要点击「Get Started」，然后按照需求下载模型。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1190-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1190-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1190.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击 Get Started</p><p>目前「Fullmoon」提供 2 种模型，分别是 1b 参数的 llama-3.2，和 3b 参数的 llama-3.2。参数愈多生成的回复就愈详细，但亦需要更多时间去生成回复。你可以视乎自己手上 iPhone 型号新旧决定下载 1b 或 3b 模型。小编手上的 iPhone 是最新 iPhone 16，因此就下载了 3b 模型。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287790" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1191-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1191-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1191.png 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲视乎电话新旧决定要使用 1b 或 3b 模型</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287791" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1194-268x580.png" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1194-268x580.png 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_1194.png 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲看见上图画面代表已安装好模型</p><br /><b>
