        <item>
            <title>黄仁勋 Chok 足样大赞华为 Mate XT    指三折叠技术「不可思议」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/21/jensen-huang-amazed-by-huawei-mate-xt/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=jensen-huang-amazed-by-huawei-mate-xt</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/21/jensen-huang-amazed-by-huawei-mate-xt/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 05:45:10 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1287911</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>NVIDIA 行政总裁黄仁勋日前在中国北京出席公司答谢迎春会，期间亲身体验华为最新推出的 Mate XT 三折叠手机 。他以「不可思议（incredible）」和「难以置信（unbelievable）」称赞 Mate XT 之设计和技术，并表示非常欣赏手机的特大荧幕，适合他用作阅读、观看影片之用，同时保有轻盈的重量。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287924" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012110148-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012110148-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2025012110148.jpg 506w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲黄仁勋接触华为 Mate XT 时面露惊讶神情，图片来源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@AATUINVEST">AATU 아아투@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287919" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250121125920-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250121125920-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250121125920.jpg 506w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲黄仁勋指华为 Mate XT 对他而言很实用，图片来源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@AATUINVEST">AATU 아아투@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287921" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250121125830-325x580.jpg" alt="" width="325" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250121125830-325x580.jpg 325w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250121125830.jpg 504w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 325px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲表示适合用作阅读，图片来源：<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@AATUINVEST">AATU 아아투@YouTube</a></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_93667"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/I-Ib6Ng-8Wk?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>黄仁勋在致辞中回顾 NVIDIA 在中国扎根超过 25 年的历程，目前公司在当地拥有近 4,000 名员工，业务分布于深圳、北京及上海等主要城市。他强调，GeForce 显示卡在中国市场的卓越表现，对辉达的全球成长举足轻重，并形容中国某种程度上「养育」了辉达的发展。</p><p>黄仁勋现场体验华为 Mate XT 三折叠手机，对其多折叠设计在阅读及观影上的灵活性予以称赞。他还拿 Mate XT 与其他智能手机对比，并用中文幽默地表示「厚度差不多嘛」。然而相关影片发布后，部分中国网友认为黄仁勋的反应过於戏剧化，留言指「演技浮夸」及「演得真像」，质疑其真诚度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1287926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/641-320x580.jpeg" alt="" width="320" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/641-320x580.jpeg 320w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/641.jpeg 496w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 320px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲黄仁勋期间以其他手机比对 Mate XT，表示厚度差不多，图片来源：<a href="https://www.6parknews.com/newspark/view.php?app=news&amp;act=view&amp;nid=706542">6park news</a></p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%96%E8%A6%8B%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA3%E6%91%BA%E6%A9%9F-%E9%BB%83%E4%BB%81%E5%8B%B3%E7%9B%B4%E5%91%BC-%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E6%80%9D%E8%AD%B0-%E9%99%B8%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8D%E8%B2%B7%E5%96%AE-%E6%BC%94%E5%BE%97%E5%A5%BD%E5%81%87-035800296.html">东森新闻</a>、<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/@AATUINVEST">AATU 아아투@YouTube</a>、<a href="https://www.ctee.com.tw/news/20250121700868-430804">工商时报</a>、<a href="https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121347/8504041">世界新闻网</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
